    CoCluster Correlation Network

    ex.cccn.matrix.Rd

    Network of relationships between genes based on clustering of ptms from the three distance metrics.

    ex.cccn.matrix

    Format

    Square matrix with 19 rows and columns:

    rows/columns

    Gene

    values

    Strength of correlation

    Source

    "created by MakeCorrelationNetwork"

    Examples

    data(ex.cccn.matrix)
